    {
      "lineNumber": 3,
      "text": "SUBJECT: FLYING SAUCERS",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 4,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 5,
      "text": "PURPOSE:",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 6,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "text": "To advise at the present time the Air Force has",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "text": "failed to arrive at any satisfactory conclusion in",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "text": "its research regarding numerous reports of flying saucers and",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "text": "flying discs sighted throughout the United States.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "DETAILS:",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "Mr. N. W. Philcox, the Bureau's Air Force Liaison",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "Representative, made arrangements through the office of",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "Major General John A. Samford, Director of Air Intelligence,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "U.S. Air Force, to receive a briefing from Commander Randall",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "Boyd of the Current Intelligence Branch, Estimates Division,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "Air Intelligence regarding the present status of Air Intelligence",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "research into the numerous reports regarding flying saucers",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "and flying discs.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "Commander Boyd advised that Air Intelligence has",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "set up at Wright Patterson Air Force Base, Ohio, the Air",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "Technical Intelligence Center which has has been established for",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "the purpose of coordinating, correlating and making research",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "into all reports regarding flying saucers and flying discs.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "He advised that Air Force research has indicated that the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "sightings of flying saucers goes back several centuries and",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "that the number of sightings reported varies with the amount",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "of publicity. He advised that immediately if publicity appears",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "in newspapers, the number of sightings reported increases",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "considerably and that citizens immediately call in reporting",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "sightings which occurred several months previously. Commander",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "Boyd stated that those reported sightings of flying saucers",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "are placed into three classifications by Air Intelligence:",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "text": "(1) Those sightings which are reported by citizens who",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "text": "claim they have seen flying saucers from the ground.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 40,
      "text": "These sightings vary in description, color and speeds.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 41,
      "text": "Very little credence is given to these sightings",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 42,
      "text": "inasmuch as in most instances they are believed to be",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 43,
      "text": "imaginative or some explainable object which actually",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 44,
      "text": "crossed through the sky.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 45,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 46,
      "text": "(2) Sightings reported by commercial or military",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 47,
      "text": "pilots. These sightings are considered more credible",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
